            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 6297,
            "text": "{\n  \"id\": \"resp_0bbc59d64c71ab84006a1503e38150819689b9bcf3492ea20e\",\n  \"object\": \"response\",\n  \"created_at\": 1779762147,\n  \"status\": \"completed\",\n  \"background\": false,\n  \"billing\": {\n    \"payer\": \"developer\"\n  },\n  \"completed_at\": 1779762160,\n  \"error\": null,\n  \"frequency_penalty\": 0.0,\n  \"incomplete_details\": null,\n  \"instructions\": \"Use the DeepWiki MCP tools to answer questions about code repositories. Be very concise.\",\n  \"max_output_tokens\": null,\n  \"max_tool_calls\": null,\n  \"model\": \"gpt-4o-2024-08-06\",\n  \"moderation\": null,\n  \"output\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"mcpl_0bbc59d64c71ab84006a1503e38c9081969bcf46d232f65c23\",\n      \"type\": \"mcp_list_tools\",\n      \"server_label\": \"deepwiki\",\n      \"tools\": [\n        {\n          \"annotations\": {\n            \"read_only\": false\n          },\n          \"description\": \"Get a list of documentation topics for a GitHub repository.\\n\\nArgs:\\n    repoName: GitHub repository in owner/repo format (e.g. \\\"facebook/react\\\")\",\n          \"input_schema\": {\n            \"properties\": {\n              \"repoName\": {\n                \"type\": \"string\"\n              }\n            },\n            \"required\": [\n              \"repoName\"\n            ],\n            \"type\": \"object\"\n          },\n          \"name\": \"read_wiki_structure\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"annotations\": {\n            \"read_only\": false\n          },\n          \"description\": \"View documentation about a GitHub repository.\\n\\nArgs:\\n    repoName: GitHub repository in owner/repo format (e.g. \\\"facebook/react\\\")\",\n          \"input_schema\": {\n            \"properties\": {\n              \"repoName\": {\n                \"type\": \"string\"\n              }\n            },\n            \"required\": [\n              \"repoName\"\n            ],\n            \"type\": \"object\"\n          },\n          \"name\": \"read_wiki_contents\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"annotations\": {\n            \"read_only\": false\n          },\n          \"description\": \"Ask any question about a GitHub repository and get an AI-powered, context-grounded response.\\n\\nArgs:\\n    repoName: GitHub repository or list of repositories (max 10) in owner/repo format\\n    question: The question to ask about the repository\",\n          \"input_schema\": {\n            \"properties\": {\n              \"repoName\": {\n                \"anyOf\": [\n                  {\n                    \"type\": \"string\"\n                  },\n                  {\n                    \"items\": {\n                      \"type\": \"string\"\n                    },\n                    \"type\": \"array\"\n                  }\n                ]\n              },\n              \"question\": {\n                \"type\": \"string\"\n              }\n            },\n            \"required\": [\n              \"repoName\",\n              \"question\"\n            ],\n            \"type\": \"object\"\n          },\n          \"name\": \"ask_question\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"mcp_0bbc59d64c71ab84006a1503e5ccac819680239f2de3eb33d2\",\n      \"type\": \"mcp_call\",\n      \"status\": \"completed\",\n      \"approval_request_id\": null,\n      \"arguments\": \"{\\\"repoName\\\":\\\"openai/openai-agents-python\\\",\\\"question\\\":\\\"What programming language is this repository written in?\\\"}\",\n      \"error\": null,\n      \"name\": \"ask_question\",\n      \"output\": \"This repository is primarily written in Python.   This is indicated by the `requires-python` field in `pyproject.toml`  and the frequent use of Python code examples throughout the documentation and examples.  \\n\\n## Evidence of Python Usage\\n\\n*   **`pyproject.toml`**: The `pyproject.toml` file explicitly states `requires-python = \\\">=3.10\\\"` , indicating that the project is built for Python environments. It also lists numerous Python dependencies such as `openai`, `pydantic`, and `requests`. \\n*   **Documentation and Examples**: The `README.md`  and various documentation files like `docs/ja/index.md`  contain Python code snippets for installation and usage of the SDK.\\n*   **Scripts and Workflows**: Python scripts are used for tasks such as translating documentation  and managing pull request labels. \\n*   **Development Tools**: The `Makefile`  and `.github/workflows/tests.yml`  show commands for `mypy` and `pytest`, which are Python-specific tools for type checking and testing, respectively.\\n\\n## Notes\\n\\nWhile the repository primarily uses Python, there are instances of shell scripts for automation and CI/CD workflows.   However, the core SDK and its functionalities are implemented in Python. \\n\\nWiki pages you might want to explore:\\n- [Overview (openai/openai-agents-python)](/wiki/openai/openai-agents-python#1)\\n- [Installation and Dependencies (openai/openai-agents-python)](/wiki/openai/openai-agents-python#12.1)\\n- [Getting Started (openai/openai-agents-python)](/wiki/openai/openai-agents-python#2)\\n\\nView this search on DeepWiki: https://deepwiki.com/search/what-programming-language-is-t_e2110f43-7fd8-42f6-b60b-7d9ab2168372\\n\",\n      \"server_label\": \"deepwiki\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"msg_0bbc59d64c71ab84006a1503f09b6481969f5423eef98cff63\",\n      \"type\": \"message\",\n      \"status\": \"completed\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"output_text\",\n          \"annotations\": [],\n          \"logprobs\": [],\n          \"text\": \"Python\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"role\": \"assistant\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"parallel_tool_calls\": true,\n  \"presence_penalty\": 0.0,\n  \"previous_response_id\": null,\n  \"prompt_cache_key\": null,\n  \"prompt_cache_retention\": \"in_memory\",\n  \"reasoning\": {\n    \"context\": null,\n    \"effort\": null,\n    \"summary\": null\n  },\n  \"safety_identifier\": null,\n  \"service_tier\": \"default\",\n  \"store\": true,\n  \"temperature\": 1.0,\n  \"text\": {\n    \"format\": {\n      \"type\": \"text\"\n    },\n    \"verbosity\": \"medium\"\n  },\n  \"tool_choice\": \"auto\",\n  \"tools\": [\n    {\n      \"type\": \"mcp\",\n      \"allowed_tools\": null,\n      \"headers\": null,\n      \"require_approval\": \"never\",\n      \"server_description\": null,\n      \"server_label\": \"deepwiki\",\n      \"server_url\": \"https://mcp.deepwiki.com/mcp\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"top_logprobs\": 0,\n  \"top_p\": 1.0,\n  \"truncation\": \"disabled\",\n  \"usage\": {\n    \"input_tokens\": 684,\n    \"input_tokens_details\": {\n      \"cached_tokens\": 0\n    },\n    \"output_tokens\": 40,\n    \"output_tokens_details\": {\n      \"reasoning_tokens\": 0\n    },\n    \"total_tokens\": 724\n  },\n  \"user\": null,\n  \"metadata\": {}\n}"
